HEADWORD: ackee
<hw>ackee</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <fr>1</fr> <def>red pear-shaped
tropical fruit with poisonous seeds; its flesh is poisonous when unripe
or overripe.</def>⟦br⟧
